<plot>This movie is about life in the projects circa 1958: Driven to the brink by her overworked and unsensitive husband and horrendously selfish children, Brooklyn-based housewife Gloria Goodman ('Kirstie Alley' (qv)) seeks a meaning to life. Suddenly, she meets Bert Kramer ('Gil Bellows' (qv)), a hipper-than-thou young writer, who shows her a new view on life... and also the possibility of a passionate romance... Will she be seduced or will she find her own path in life? Or maybe both?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?453306</url></doc>
